Wertheim Schroder and Co Inc said itappointed Steven Kotler, 40, president of the investmentbanking and securities firm.    Wertheim said Kotler has been a managing director andmember of the executive committee of the firm, which is 50 pctowned by &lt;Schroders PLC> of the United Kingdom and 50 pct ownedby Wertheim partners. Reuter&#3;